metadata.editComments: The first time I heard this song, at the intro I thought it was a Spanish cover of "Jealous Guy" by John Lennon (because of the chord progression G–D–D7–em...). Luckily Enrique didn't plagiarize the em6 chord (borrowed from Lydian) nor did he use Mixolydian b6 in the chorus lmao.

And this part seems it's going to sound like "No me digas que no 2.0" with Wisin & Yandel but in bachata version. But what the hell, no matter how generic this song seems, I love it and it brings me back good memories.
